710611f-a.title: Manhattan: 11th Avenue - 28th Street (West)
710611f-a.text:
Eleventh Avenue, north from West 28th Street. At 30th
Street appears the elevated roadbed carrying the New York
Central Railroad tracks around their yards. View 2 is
oloser to same, being from 29th Street (left). No. 3
details the gas station at the S. W. corner of 30th St.
1-2: August 25, 1940
3: February 7, 1932
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTION3
